## 10.1 Monorepo Root

unicore/
├── .cursorrules                         ← this file (read by Cursor automatically)
├── UNICORE_MASTER_PROMPT.md             ← phase-by-phase implementation prompts
├── .github/
│   └── workflows/
│       ├── api.yml                      ← NestJS CI/CD
│       ├── web.yml                      ← Next.js web CI/CD
│       └── admin.yml                    ← Next.js admin CI/CD
├── apps/
│   ├── api/                             ← NestJS (standalone deployable)
│   ├── web/                             ← Next.js institution portal (standalone)
│   └── admin/                           ← Next.js super admin (standalone)
├── packages/
│   ├── database/                        ← Prisma schema + migrations + seeds
│   ├── types/                           ← Shared TypeScript interfaces
│   ├── ui/                              ← Shared shadcn/ui components
│   ├── utils/                           ← Shared utilities + formatters
│   └── config/                          ← ESLint, TS, Tailwind base configs
├── docker-compose.yml                   ← Local dev: postgres, redis, minio, mailhog
├── docker-compose.prod.yml              ← Production compose
├── turbo.json                           ← Turborepo pipeline config
├── pnpm-workspace.yaml
└── package.json                         ← Root scripts

